Package com.flipkart.bean

Class FlipFitCustomer

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitCustomer
public class FlipFitCustomer extends Object
The FlipFitCustomer class represents a customer in the FlipFit system. It includes details such as weight, age, gender, customer name, phone, address, and customer ID.
